OL,3,CBergerac back in Jersey as filming for
OL,4,Csecond series gets underway
OL,6,FActors and film crews have been
OL,7,Fspotted in St Brelade's Bay as
OL,8,Fshooting for the second series of
OL,9,FBergerac gets underway in Jersey.
OL,11,FThe popular detective drama was
OL,12,Frebooted more than 30 years after the
OL,13,Foriginal show's run and became the
OL,14,Fsecond-highest-rated programme on
OL,15,FU&DRAMA when it premiered in February,
OL,16,Fwith 2.4 million consolidated viewers.
OL,18,FIt was also sold to several
OL,19,Finternational broadcasters and one TV
OL,20,Fcritic described it as "a love letter
OL,21,Fto the original series".
