OL,3,CBergerac back in Jersey as filming for
OL,4,Csecond series gets underway
OL,6,FNow filming a second series, Executive
OL,7,FProducer Brian Constantine hopes that
OL,8,Fviewers will spot more local locations
OL,9,Fas the show continues.
OL,11,FHe says: "It's amazing to be back in
OL,12,FJersey and so far, things are going
OL,13,Fwell. It's such a good feeling on set.
OL,15,F"There is no Bergerac without Jersey,
OL,16,Fit's one of the characters on its own,
OL,17,Fso it's paramount that we keep coming
OL,18,Fback and including it as the home of
OL,19,FBergerac."
