OL,3,CBergerac back in Jersey as filming for
OL,4,Csecond series gets underway
OL,6,FThe show will return to screens in
OL,7,F2026, featuring familiar figures such
OL,8,Fas Damien Molony and Zoe Wanamaker,
OL,9,Fwho will reprise their roles as Jim
OL,10,FBergerac and Charlie Hungerford.
OL,12,FThere will also be some new faces as
OL,13,Fseveral actors, including Lesley Sharp
OL,14,Fand Adrian Edmondson, join the
OL,15,Fproduction.
OL,17,FIn the second series, it is a year on
OL,18,Fand Bergerac is starting to put his
OL,19,Flife back together after the loss of
OL,20,Fhis wife.
