OL,3,CBergerac back in Jersey as filming for
OL,4,Csecond series gets underway
OL,6,FHe meets someone, but soon has to get
OL,7,Fto work after a groom is found
OL,8,Fmurdered in a hotel room.
OL,10,FDirector Joss Agnew says Molony
OL,11,F"knocked it out of the park" in series
OL,12,Fone and will explore "darker
OL,13,Fterritory" as the storyline develops.
OL,15,FHe adds: "It's such a special island
OL,16,Fand it's interesting to explore
OL,17,Fsomewhere so beautiful where such dark
OL,18,Fthings happen."
